{"tid":1208022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教協認為現時社會氣氛急劇惡化 發動本周全港罷課","createTime":"2019-06-12T08:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T08:54:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee109716d60815530815c801596d983a404193b","tid":1208022,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:41:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462368-20190612.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462368-20190612.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LMVY6Z7nIekaHefcscWgVZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=4acce59d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462368-20190612.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1aaca144\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462368-20190612.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n教協認為現時社會氣氛急劇惡化 發動本周全港罷課<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-12 HKT 16:36<br />\n 分享工具  facebook  twitter<br />\n教協宣布發動本周全港罷課。<br />\n<br />\n教協發聲明說，政府不惜一切硬推惡法，立法會主席梁君彥不斷加開會議配合政府，做法必須譴責。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，現時有大批市民於金鐘一帶聚集，教協強烈要求警方克制，並強調警方使用過分武力，將令市民和政府的關係推進深淵。<br />\n<br />\n教協認為，現時社會氣氛正急劇惡化，決定宣布發動本周全港罷課，呼籲大專院校仍有課堂的教師配合罷課，並提供日後補課安排；又呼籲中學教師與校方商討，訂出罷課具體安排；小學教師回校罷教，在課堂上向學生解釋事件；而幼稚園及幼兒園教師則要緊守崗位，照顧年幼學童。<br />\n<br />\n教協呼籲校方理解罷課罷教是重要決定，希望支持校長和教師的選擇。家長可以自行決定是否讓子女回校。"},{"pid":"844ee1c6a3129b9b77edbc79563060dc849d113d","tid":1208022,"uid":173849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ea1b3e142acafc80da187455871ae24bc4275d","tid":1208022,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"I can do it all year"},{"pid":"871329776b14553eb4c3e8ca7cdb2cfe3f6028ff","tid":1208022,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f19dd83881bfac42d947650298689b341ecab8a","tid":1208022,"uid":186704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"場外應繼續三罷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a7848c52037de5494a132343c5b63fff3ced77","tid":1208022,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fec101c6e06e6cb61d938e85bce3f2a550d87fe","tid":1208022,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}